## Why `event.systemPromptOptions.selectedTools = ["delegate"]` is inert

| Step | What happens | Effect on tools |
|------|-------------|-----------------|
| 1 | Handler mutates `event.systemPromptOptions.selectedTools` | Mutates local event object only |
| 2 | Handler returns `{ systemPrompt: "..." }` | Only `systemPrompt` string is read |
