| 4 | `agent-session.js` processes result | Only reads `.messages` and `.systemPrompt` |
| 5 | `_runAgentPrompt` called with messages | Still uses `this.agent.state.tools` — unchanged |
| 6 | LLM receives system prompt via `buildSystemPrompt` | Built from `_baseSystemPromptOptions.selectedTools` — unchanged |

**No code path propagates `event.systemPromptOptions` modifications back to agent state or the next prompt build.**

