## Dependencies

- **`subagent-runner.ts`** imports from `@earendil-works/pi-ai` (getModel), `@earendil-works/pi-coding-agent` (createAgentSession, DefaultResourceLoader, etc.), and `./activity-feed.ts`, `./types.ts`, `../token-saver.ts`
